cdata.name: Cygnus
cdata.desc: Cygnus was developed in order to provide a stable, and easy to use cryptocurrency for the community. Cygnus is a PoS/Hybrid coin that allows users to earns rewards by mining or by staking CYG coins owned. In order to providea totallyegalitarian and fair distributionprocess, a bounty and airdrop process was developed before the launch.
